<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234687>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Macrostomum heyuanensis Wang & Sun, n. sp., ventral view: (A) body in whole; (B) profile of the tail; (C) copulatory apparatus; (D) penis stylet; (E) sperm." ;
